  "text": "Then the lines of spiraling light energy, do they originate from a position toward the center of the earth and read outward from that point? I am wrong. The pyramid shape is a collector which draws the in-streaming energy from what you would term the bottom or base and allows this energy to spiral upward in a line with the apex of this shape. This is also true if a pyramid shape is upended. The energy is not earth energy as we understand your question, but is light energy which is omnipresent.",
